subject: Basketball
organizations: Rutgers, The State University of New Jersey
lead_paragraph: Matee Ajavon had 21 points, 5 assists and 5 rebounds to lead No. 5 Rutgers to its eighth consecutive win, a 69-47 victory at home against Seton Hall on Saturday.
